name: Software Development Management: What makes a good software developer?
caption: softwaredevmanagement.blogspot.com

data.message: I Don't trust such a Guide. What makes a Good Anyone Is the ability to resolve problems. nothing more and nothing less. Technical skills comes last as it will be an execution for a solution you have. and right now it's very easy to learn any programming language.
I agree,know how to solve problems is a critical key to differentiate between good developer and developer but technical skills also important it reduce the time required to solve those problems ..
